ame amount of damage. This only really matters if you think you can kill them fast enough to where taking dmg later (bof first) will make a difference because you may be able to kill them before they break manasink, or against lifetaps they will gain hp later in the fight as opposed to maybe 100-200 earlier by breaking manasink first. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvexxed.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vexxed</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/27/01 6:47 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: spells</span><hr size=1> I usually stick to Lures only until they run. The speed of Draughts &gt; Lures when your target is fleeing.<br>
