<br>
Sup guys!<br>
<br>
There is some luck involved in PVP since non-lures can do some big damage if they hit full. Your best bet is to use Lures and the first lure does not always win (wizard vs wizard). Standing next to each other nuking lures is not much of a battle. 1 battle can take an hour. If you're at 25% heath and your opponent is 50% you better get out of range fast and rebuff. You have to use your draughts and hope to get lucky for killshots sometimes, when your opponents start to flee or gate. <br>
<br>
Manaburn should be fun in PvP =) <br>
<br>
Shyner<br>
