I am a 40 necro. Just my two cents... hehe most wizzies i pk i start out with defuff then pet attack and darkness spell (takes away sow if they got it). Throw a dot maybe two (venom of the snake rules!!!) and then my harm shield. What is harm shield like 20 to 30 seconds i cant take damage?<br>
<br>
hehe they blast me with all thier might and i laugh.  No one debuffs me or anything usually??? and if they do i have vision spells or something up so it drops first.  If the wizzy goes after my pet with root or whatever i look for it and suck life or something before i damage shield and watch the hp go down. <br>
<br>
If they dont mess with my pet... i still watch thier hp go down with at least one dot on them and my pet bashing them as they try to cast. As soon as they see they cant blast me and try gating or really focusing on my pet i drop the shield and suck life once or twice and its pretty close to over.<br>
<br>
If i have the suprise and they dont have p vs p spells up its over quickly. I can pretty much fart around and use whatever strategy i want (suprise rules!)<br>
<br>
Guess my mr, cr, and fr that are high rule too vs wizzies. About 100 to 130 on each.<br>
<br>
I might not have the greatest strategy?!? But it works well for me as I win most my fights. Kinda sucks though... after lvl 34ish I can see my great p vs p powers fading vs other classes.<br>
